{"tid":296270,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我同條女講一齊申請公屋 第二日就同我分手","createTime":"2017-06-24T12:19:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-24T14:50:22.000Z","uid":103616,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"896259989e63e4136181d38f2969c82beebc5cd4","tid":296270,"uid":103616,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:19:44.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n小弟出身微寒 做緊基層工<br />\n中學畢業之後一直都有個女朋友<br />\n都同佢識咗四五年<br />\n<br />\n上個禮拜我決定同佢拉埋天窗<br />\n去打冷舖食完飯就同佢求婚<br />\n佢接過咗隻戒指之後本來都好開心<br />\n<br />\n於是我同佢去散步 順便講下我對將來嘅規劃<br />\n諗住同佢去註冊之後擺幾圍酒 tum掂四大長老<br />\n就一齊去申請公屋<br />\n<br />\n點知佢塊面黑咗一黑 即刻話自己唔舒服要番屋企休息<br />\n第二日whatsapp話同我分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n四五年嘅感情就係因為一間公屋告吹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我本來就係一個基層 打緊基層工<br />\n你明知架 點解仲要同我一齊咁耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你明知我買唔起樓 點解仲要同我一齊咁耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解要用呢四年嘅時間黎欺騙我？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪窮人特別好蝦啲？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07d3122ce41e9a6fcf0e61498784abb4dbe9de31","tid":296270,"uid":75359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:21:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12cdd4f2d2526dfef0cb343df673eed7c5a1df1f","tid":296270,"uid":117751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:38:05.000Z","msg":"i know that feel bro<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8962130a1b1e71e4177cd816e37b8fa0fc62ea04","tid":296270,"uid":9121,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T12:55:47.000Z","msg":"窮人冇資格拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca88a009fabf209e983ecaed66da475b1ba16b31","tid":296270,"uid":93903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T13:44:32.000Z","msg":"雖然條女係好現實 但窮是原罪 <br />\n千其唔好生仔"},{"pid":"98136b617ba273defc95da3055f89fd29e3ea5c8","tid":296270,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:47:24.000Z","msg":"好事嚟嘅"},{"pid":"2831de9adbc1d7c29a2486bd0ce5582bb395ddf0","tid":296270,"uid":112483,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-24T14:50:22.000Z","msg":"邊關事<br />\n<br />\n你幾年前申請定，注完冊入得伙咪無事，而家申請要等幾多年你知唔知"}]}